<kickstart>

<description>
MPI libraries modules files
http://www.mcs.anl.gov/research/projects/mpi/mpich1
http://www.mcs.anl.gov/research/projects/mpich2
http://www.open-mpi.org
http://mvapich.cse.ohio-state.edu
